FBIS4-137 "drafr064_a_94003" FBIS-AFR-94-064 Daily Report 2 Apr 1994 CENTRAL AFRICA Chad Foreign Minister Denies Iranian Assistance Sought Foreign Minister Denies Iranian Assistance Sought AB0304203594 Libreville Africa No. 1 in French 0730 GMT 2 Apr 94 AB0304203594 Libreville Africa No. 1 French BFN [Text] In Chad, Foreign Minister Fakadi Lokna has denied reports that Iran's assistance had been sought regarding the exploitation of Chadian oil.
